Class BinaryNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>

    T - The type of data element contained within the node (and binary tree).
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    INode<T>
    public class BinaryNode<T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>>
extends SuperNode<T>
implements INode<T>
    Main super class for nodes contained within binary based tree data structures. Contains common functionality for different binary trees.

    Tom Esser
